{"tid":478860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再見了光頭　南韓稱發現治脫髮方法","createTime":"2017-11-24T13:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T16:06:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":217,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"4793db15766e33432f89dc25a4067ae65f3faf85","tid":478860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/photo/bknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001_01p.jpg?20171124163120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171124%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171124163120&h=7a5bb8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實驗結果顯示崔康烈研發的物質有效治療脫髮。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n許多人踏入某個年齡階段，脫髮便會成為其中一個最令他們思緒煩躁的問題。南韓科學團隊近期發現，導致脫髮的原因在於一種擾亂基因表現的複雜蛋白質組合。團隊主管崔康烈（Choi Kang Yeol，音譯）於是對症下藥研發試驗性的物質，上月更通過於老鼠身上的實驗，找出治療方法，有望成為「光頭一族」的救星。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/photo/bknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001_03b.jpg?20171124163120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171124%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20171124163120&h=4f842172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n崔康烈有望成為打救「光頭佬」的偉人。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n是次研究由南韓政府科學技術部門資助，並由延世大學教授團隊領導。團隊表示，早前在部分動物體內發現「CXXC5」蛋白質與一些雜亂無章的蛋白質互相綑綁，它們會中斷Wnt訊息傳遞路徑，從而影響毛囊生長及再生程序。<br />\n<br />\n就着這突破性的發現，崔康烈偕其夥伴研發全新的生物化學物質「PTD-DBM」，以防CXXC5與其他雜亂蛋白質連結。他們早前在老鼠身上進行為期28天的實驗（圖2），將物質塗上老鼠表皮，發現老鼠的毛囊果然明顯增加。研究結果已獲刊登於皮膚病學醫學期刊。<br />\n<br />\n崔康烈指出，日後應用新研發物質的治療不但可以令毛髮再生，更有助加快生長速度；同時，治療有望助受損皮膚組織重生。"},{"pid":"91baeaa3ea57bf6f66dd1e77b0463f4bd0e2208b","tid":478860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/bknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171124%2Fbknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001.html&d=SgNnyH76waw9HssOd3gUT7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=51f7d2fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/bknint-20171124132624592-1124_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2cc73e9dbe2d5f97e537a8653e947c246c268c60","tid":478860,"uid":41245,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"可唔可以加鬚"},{"pid":"8553bd0d57580701d3bcbd95d9b83e4b530f3f78","tid":478860,"uid":27251,"like":400,"dislike":2,"score":398,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"仲諗住拉落去會見到個專家係禿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f274342d8aa14b930118d7858dea3527b241d76","tid":478860,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住拉落去會見到個專家係禿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢就快光頭"},{"pid":"d8c9d2bb859d9996e67d0db88f9b242ba3a69d7b","tid":478860,"uid":71725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99c77ae44608a27b1132f797f9c2f2c4c0ba8ed7","tid":478860,"uid":124899,"like":55,"dislike":5,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"如果慳，一定要比諾貝爾生物及醫學獎佢"},{"pid":"a99aec8c54b33a586821666491b36d0f3272d527","tid":478860,"uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"好消息，加油，可以幫到好多人"},{"pid":"6c8a9f3ebb3af0660f9b75c4842e6138a3425074","tid":478860,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"有啲失望 本來諗住個專家都係咁樣<br />\n所以先立志做研究解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 造福世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b2587b271d97b119be25c536e7bbd4f28a4907","tid":478860,"uid":38938